'''開放教育資源'''（{{lang-en|Open educational resources}}，縮寫為 OER），採用[[内容开放|開放授權]]的[[教材|教材]]，通常是數位化的資料，可供教學、學習、研究之用，如常用的[[創用CC授權|創用CC授權]]，使用者只要遵守授權條款，便不會構成侵犯版權。雖然開放教育資源，不能讓學習者因此得到學位，但是它對於[[開放教育|開放教育]]（Open education）與[[遠距教學|遠距教學]]有很大的幫助，也有助於使教育資源的分配更加平等<ref>{{cite journal|author=Bozkurt, A., Akgun-Ozbek, E., Onrat-Yilmazer, S., Erdogdu, E., Ucar, H., Guler, E., Sezgin, S., Karadeniz, A., Sen, N., Goksel-Canbek, N., Dincer, G. D., Ari, S.,& Aydin, C. H.|date=2015|title=Trends in Distance Education Research: A Content Analysis of Journals 2009-2013|journal=International Review of Research in Open and Distributed Learning|volume=16|issue=1|pages=330–363|url=https://www.academia.edu/11056576/Trends_in_Distance_Education_Research_A_Content_Analysis_of_Journals_2009-2013|access-date=2017-05-10|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327142925/https://www.academia.edu/11056576/Trends_in_Distance_Education_Research_A_Content_Analysis_of_Journals_2009-2013|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

开放和促进开放教育资源往往是被提供替代或增强的[[教育|教育]][[范式|范式]]的愿望所驱动<ref>{{cite web|last=Sanchez|first=Claudia|title=The use of technological resources for education: a new professional competency for teachers|url=https://blogs.intel.com/intel-education-solutions/2012/11/30/the-use-of-technological-resources-for-education-a-new-professional-competency-for-teachers/|work=Intel® Learning Series blog|publisher=Intel Corporation|accessdate=23 April 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130329000906/http://blogs.intel.com/intel-education-solutions/2012/11/30/the-use-of-technological-resources-for-education-a-new-professional-competency-for-teachers/|archivedate=2013-03-29}}</ref>。

[[MIT_OpenCourseWare|MIT OpenCourseWare]]对全球开放教育资源的发展有着相当大的推动作用。[[英國公開大學|英國公開大學]]在远程教育领域的开放教育资源建设方面也有着非常大的影响。

